Uses of Package
net.objectzoo.delegates

  • Packages that use net.objectzoo.delegates 
    Package Description
    net.objectzoo.delegates
    This package contains the delegates of the Events4J API.
    net.objectzoo.delegates.adapters
    This package contains support classes that can be used to wrap standard delegates to be asynchronous.
    net.objectzoo.delegates.impl
    This package contains support classes that can be used to implement AsyndAction or AsyncFunction delegates.
    net.objectzoo.events
    This package contains the events of the Events4J API.
    net.objectzoo.events.impl
    This package contains support classes that implement EventDelegates ready to be used.
  • Classes in net.objectzoo.delegates used by net.objectzoo.delegates 
    Class and Description
    Action
    An Action is a reference to a procedure without return value that can be invoked synchronously similar to a regular Java method call.

    An Action0 is a reference to a procedure without return value that can be invoked synchronously similar to a regular Java method call.
